{
  "title": "Spicy Gooey Corn Flour Stir-fry",
  "description": "This Spicy Gooey Corn Flour Stir-fry is a show-off Italian dish featuring corn flour that's kneadable and high-protein-friendly, perfect for breakfast or lunch.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
  "diet": null,
